      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for those. i've heard some mixed things about the more urban areas nearby though. like, are there any districts i should probably avoid if i'm looking for that stability and high achievement? i just want to make sure we don't end up in an area thats too unpredictable or has too much crime/instability for kids.",
