      "content": "that makes sense. i've noticed that when i look at certain neighborhoods with more diverse populations, the school ratings and safety reports seem a lot more hit or miss. do you think there's a link between the demographics of a district and the kind of stability/achievement level i'm looking for? just trying to be realistic about what to expect.",
